## D. Integration

| Concern | Primary doc |
|---------|------------|
| Map generation, zones, edges, VOID devour | `MapGDD.md` |
| Foe types, AI, evolution, loot hooks | `FOES.gdd` |
| Node content, day cycle, team build, shelter functions | `NODES.gdd` |
| Wonder items, tags, cooldowns, item catalog | `ITEMS.gdd` |
| ATK/DEF formulas, engineering conventions | `KNOWLEDGE.md` |
| Per-character abilities, stats, visuals | `Docs/<CharacterName>.gdd` |

